-28T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個睇過個醫生叫黃雅信，睇完一次就斷尾，到以家差唔多十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打可以試下</blockquote>食藥定做手術？</blockquote><br />\n冇做過手術呀，我個陣去睇佢比咗半個月藥我食，之後再去覆診，佢比多1個月藥我看門口就冇再見過個醫生，同埋買咗部空氣清新機，有時空氣太差個鼻痕痕地開，我另外有枝噴鼻嘅藥係看門口，轉天氣打乞痴用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：小學個陣每日都流鼻水流到個鼻有八成時間都塞住，睇完之後呢十年都冇再返發真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望幫到你地"},{"pid":"3aafd8beff17df2fa53aca482867e82908798fd7","tid":681264,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071855f8af8c31882edcedab4fee1070f78d0345","tid":681264,"uid":155080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1acca5e8a92e05acb49c47f413c31097b75340f4","tid":681264,"uid":77461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b1b958d88cb689ff9c914fc11e75d233d334998","tid":681264,"uid":127466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:00:29.000Z","msg":"每日用鹽水洗鼻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"真係得？<br />\n一起身已經痕到仆街<br />\n一日用幾包紙巾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"耳鼻喉醫生都教人用鹽水洗鼻"},{"pid":"cedf007b4a245c8c6bc4bdf371e173d081adc42b","tid":681264,"uid":155080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12497067a079fb5dadf2fa437fea9024eeb6dd4c","tid":681264,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e56a25b011f56b828551480625fdf695a3a9777","tid":681264,"uid":155080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"Google下鼻中隔成型術/粘膜下隔切除術，我喺政府醫院做，幾百蚊就解決晒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"※手術不能解決的問題1.非鼻中隔彎曲導致的鼻塞。2.過敏性鼻炎導致的症狀如鼻癢、噴嚏、後鼻漏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma